race.description: Spry Civil Construction Stake Pr1 Division1
race.comment: BOOTERSTOWN (4) is a talented dog who is a winner of seven races and filled a minor placing latest when third at Angle Park (31.01). Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Can measure up this time. WEBLEC PEBBLES (5) flew around 395m at this track in 22.35 three back then has been in the money the last two since. Expected to feature on best figures. DAINTREE BULLET (2) was unfancied last time out but hit the ground running to lead all the way, scoring by 1.3 lengths (30.88) at Angle Park in a Grade 6 over 530m. The form out of his last race has been franked. Has definite claims. GOLD LOKI (7) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.

runners.name: Weblec Pebbles
runners.owners: Weblang Synd A Langton,J Weber,N Loechel
